 on Five Daily Prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"The parable of the five prayers is that of a river running...\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20316,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-nawawi-forenoon-prayer-salat-duha\/","url_meta":{"origin":14361,"position":3},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Forenoon Prayer, Salat al-Duha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\"It is enough to perform two cycles of forenoon prayer.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/sunan-of-sleeping-and-waking\/","url_meta":{"origin":14361,"position":4},"title":"Sunan of sleeping and waking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Whoever goes to sleep in a state of purity will have an angel over his head.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sunnah \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sunnah \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/sunnah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14180,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/worship-allah-in-fear-of-hellfire-and-hope-of-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":14361,"position":5},"title":"Worshiping Allah in fear and hope","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"They arise from their beds and they supplicate their Lord in fear and hope, and they spend from what We have provided them.\" --Surah As-Sajda 32:16","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14361","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14361"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14361\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14361"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14361"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14361"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}